{"word":"H830 - אַשְׁפֹּת - ʼashpôth - ash-pohth' - Dung","slug":"H830","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אַשְׁפֹּת</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼashpôth"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ash-pohth'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Dung"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E4;&#x05EA;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05EA;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05EA; - 'ashpo&#x0302;th  'ashpo&#x0302;th  sh<sup>e</sup>pho&#x0302;th</b> - <i>ash-pohth', ash-pohth', shef-ohth'</i><p/>Plural of a noun of the same form as <a href=\"#/H827\">H827</a>, from <a href=\"#/H8192\">H8192</a> (in the sense of <i>scraping</i>); a heap of <i>rubbish</i> or <i>filth: - </i>dung (hill)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4942\">H4942</a>, <a href=\"#/H8239\">H8239</a>, <a href=\"#/H8240\">H8240</a>"}]}